</div><div class="widget-area footer-widgets-6 footer-widget-area"><section id="custom_html-4" class="widget_text widget widget_custom_html"><div class="widget_text widget-wrap"><div class="textwidget custom-html-widget"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/chocchildrens"><img src="./(OCD)_files/social-media-facebook.png" width="32" height="32" alt="facebook" class="alignleft social-icon"></a>
